      "en": "Volume 24 Biographies 16: Lu Bian",
      "raw": "卷24 列傳第16 盧辯 Volume 24 Biographies 16: Lu Bian"
    },
    "sentenceCount": 126,
    "translatedCount": 0,
    "glossarySize": 40194,
    "scrapedAt": "2026-04-25T21:58:09.607Z",
